    <section class="privacy-section">
        <h2>Definition of Terms</h2>
        <p>For the purposes of this Privacy Policy:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Institution</b> refers to General de Jesus College (GJC).</li>
            <li><b>Platform</b> refers to the Iskolar ni Simeon research repository.</li>
            <li><b>Research Papers</b> refers to academic works, research publications, and scholarly content.</li>
            <li><b>Authors</b> refers to students, faculty, and researchers who submit their work.</li>
            <li><b>Users</b> refers to individuals with authorized GJC accounts accessing the platform.</li>
