    <section class="privacy-section">
        <h2>1. Research Paper Protection</h2>
        <p>We implement strict measures to protect your intellectual property:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access is restricted to verified GJC account holders only</li>
            <li>Digital watermarking of downloaded documents</li>
            <li>Secure storage with encryption</li>
            <li>Access logging and monitoring</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="privacy-section">
        <h2>2. Data Collection and Usage</h2>
        <p>We collect and maintain:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Author information (name)</li>
            <li>Research paper metadata and content</li>
            <li>Authentication credentials</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="privacy-section">
        <h2>3. Access Control</h2>
        <p>We ensure controlled access through:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>GJC institutional email verification</li>
            <li>Role-based access control (student, faculty, administrator)</li>
            <li>Session management and automatic timeouts</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="privacy-section">
        <h2>4. Distribution Restrictions</h2>
        <p>To protect research papers:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Sharing outside the platform is prohibited</li>
            <li>Bulk downloads are monitored and restricted</li>
            <li>Copyright notices are embedded in all documents</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
